videos.description: Jayhawks' Lagerald Vick hooks it to Udoka Azubuike who throws it down.
videos.headline: Kansas' Azubuike starts game with a dunk

videos.description: Lagerald Vick finds Udoka Azubike again early in the first half for his second dunk of the game.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Azubuike throws it down again

videos.description: Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk drives but gets denied by Nebraska's Duby Okeke.
videos.headline: Huskers' Okeke swats away driving layup

videos.description: Lagerald Vick intercepts a pass and sends it off to Devonte' Graham who swishes the 3.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' steal leads to Graham three

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike's dunk is denied by Nebraska's Duby Okeke's great defense.
videos.headline: Okeke denies Kansas dunk

videos.description: Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk feeds the ball to Udoka Azubuike who stuffs it home.
videos.headline: Azubuike jumps up for a two-handed slam

videos.description: Lagerald Vick intercepts a pass and drives it in for a layup.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Vick goes coast-to-coast

videos.description: Thomas Allen drains an easy 3-pointer to tie up the game at 51 in the second half.
videos.headline: Nebraska's Allen sinks easy three

videos.description: Devonte' Graham lobs the ball up and Udoka Azubuike who slams it down.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Azubuike with an alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike throws it down over Huskers' Isaiah Roby for his 5th dunk of the night.
videos.headline: Kansas' Azubuike dunks it over Roby

videos.description: James Palmer Jr. drains a 3-pointer for a 7-0 run.
videos.headline: Nebraska's Palmer sinks deep three

videos.description: Devonte' Graham lobs it high up in the air for Lagerald Vick to slam it home.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Vick slams down an alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Devonte' Graham quickly passes it off to Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk who drains the game-winning 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Mykhailiuk swishes game-winning three
